OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist and fog quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave a bright morning
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells. Cloud may tend to
OL,8,Fincrease throughout the day making the
OL,9,Fsunshine hazy. Feeling warm in the
OL,10,Fsunshine and light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry overnight with a
OL,13,Fmix of cloud and clear spells. Under
OL,14,Fthe clearer skies it will turn chilly
OL,15,Fwith the odd mist and fog patch.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FMist and fog quickly clearing
OL,18,Fto leave a fine and dry day with
OL,19,Fplenty of sunshine. Warm in the
OL,20,Fsunshine and light breezes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
