OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FRemaining dry and settled during the
OL,7,Ffinal days of April with spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine. Feeling warm initially
OL,9,Falthough winds strengthening by
OL,10,FWednesday making it feel a little
OL,11,Fcooler.
